\par }\pard \qj \fi-266\li266\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx266\faauto\rin0\lin266\itap0 {\fs20 2.\tab Making a category of \'93the emotions\'94 is a common-sense way of organizing descriptions of our experience. However, it could be argued that \'93emotions\'94
