 position (i..e., describe her group socialization theory and some of the evidence she adduces to support it). Then critique her theory by describing alternative theories and empirical research supporting the notion that parents do affect their children
\rquote s development. You don\rquote t have to describe specific details of specific studies\emdash but your critique must be empirically based as well as theoretically based.
